title: OpeningScene
---
Last night… yeah. That happened.
Hey. Wake up.
You cannot stay here forever.
You need to find your keys if you want to go home.
They are not all in one place. Of course they are not.
Ask around. Listen carefully. People say more than they mean to.
Four truths are hidden in this post-party.
Find all four… and you will find your way out.
